{"lastModified":1752593302908,"uri":"c::30234707298::vessel::d5cca442-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Montenegro\n\nGulet Kaptan Sevket is a stunning traditional Turkish gulet, perfect for private yacht charters in Montenegro. At 29 meters in length, this elegant vessel offers an intimate and exclusive sailing experience along the Adriatic coastline. Whether you’re planning a family holiday, a small group getaway, or a special occasion, Kaptan Sevket combines comfort, tradition, and exceptional service.\n\nWith 6 en-suite cabins (4 doubles and 2 twins), the gulet accommodates up to 12 guests, making it ideal for private charters. The spacious deck areas feature sunbathing loungers and a shaded outdoor dining area, creating the perfect setting to relax and enjoy Montenegro’s breathtaking scenery.\n\nOnboard, a dedicated crew of four provides impeccable service throughout your journey. From the captain expertly navigating the Adriatic coast to the chef crafting gourmet Mediterranean meals, every detail is designed to make your trip unforgettable.\n\nGulet Kaptan Sevket is not only a symbol of traditional craftsmanship but also a gulet with a rich sailing history. It has competed in the Bodrum Regatta in multiple editions, achieving victories that highlight its performance and elegance. Adding to its prestige, Kaptan Sevket hosted an exclusive interview with tennis legend Novak Djokovic in 2024 for GQ.","blueprint":{"name":"KAPTAN SEVKET","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca442-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c690f070-f524-11ef-aaa2-69d5c2d60276/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca442-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c6802790-f524-11ef-aaa2-69d5c2d60276/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca442-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c6b98710-f524-11ef-aaa2-69d5c2d60276/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca442-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::ass